{
  "texts": [
    "The classification and regression parts are essential for the proposed model.",
    "The classification part helps to identify promising drug combinations.",
    "By knowing whether two drugs are likely to have a synergistic, antagonistic, or additive effect, as we focus on the most promising combinations.",
    "While the regression part provides a more precise estimate of the interaction effect.",
    "This can be used to rank different drug combinations and select the most effective ones."
  ]
}